download link

jdk-8u321-windows-i586.exe

download and extract on C:\Devops_softwares folder
java you will get 2 folder 
jdk
jre

add path in windows system

#search for control panel --> advnace system setting --> environment variables --> system varialbe --> new 
#Name: JAVA_HOME                                    # here you need to add only Jdk without bin
#path: C:\Devops_softwares\Java\jdk1.8.0_321

Once add "JAVA_HOME" VARIABLE update ,add on "Path" variable --> on path we need to add till /bin for both Jdk and Jre

#Path: 
add :
#C:\Devops_softwares\Java\jdk1.8.0_321\bin
#C:\Devops_softwares\Java\jre1.8.0_321\bin

like on "Path" -->click on New and add jdk and jre paths

click on OK and open CMD and execute

#java -version

java version "1.8.0_321"
Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (build 1.8.0_321-b07)
Java HotSpot(TM) Client VM (build 25.321-b07, mixed mode)

If java showing as sth issue java not able to show version or some issue close CMD and and reopen and check

